    feat: add Dev tab to frontend ΓÇö runtime controls, API audit, self-healing dashboard
    
    New Dev tab (gear icon in nav bar) provides:
      - Connectivity: live status of all services (Ollama, Qdrant, Kimi, Opus, DB)
      - Runtime: pause/resume/hot-reload controls without stopping Grace
      - API Audit: scan all registered APIs and check health status
      - Diagnostic: view 4-layer diagnostic engine state
      - Self-Healing: trigger healing actions, view healing log
      - Quick Actions sidebar: one-click hot-reload, pause, resume, heal
    
    Also fixes health indicator: checks llm_running (actual API field name)
    instead of ollama_running (was always showing 'Partial')
    
    Co-authored-by: aaron031291 <aaron031291@users.noreply.github.com>
